These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 9

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-1::.
City: venice, edinburgh, san-francisco, nizza
4 different pets are kept: ferret, guinea-pig, hamster, rat
1. the owner of the rat is not to the right of the owner of the ferret##8
2. the owner of the rat is on the right of the person traveling to venice##1
3. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left or right of the person traveling to san-francisco##3
4. the person traveling to nizza is somewhere to the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##5
5. the person traveling to nizza is not to the left of the owner of the rat##8
6. the owner of the hamster is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to edinburgh##5
7. the person traveling to edinburgh is somewhere between the person traveling to venice and the owner of the guinea-pig##7
8. the person traveling to edinburgh and the owner of the rat have the same parity positions##9
9. the person traveling to san-francisco and the owner of the ferret have different parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Nationality   | venice | edinburgh | san-francisco     | nizza |
| Pet           | hamster   | rat     | guinea-pig | ferret  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, coffee, cola, tea
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, bolivar, havana, tiparillo
1. the vegafina-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
2. the tiparillo-smoker and the person drinking coffee have the same parity positions##9
3. the bolivar-smoker is not to the right of the havana-smoker##8
4. the vegafina-smoker is not to the right of the person drinking tea##8
5. the vegafina-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person drinking almond-milk##5
6. the person drinking almond-milk is somewhere to the right of the bolivar-smoker##5
7. the person drinking coffee is somewhere to the right of the person drinking almond-milk##5
8. the person drinking tea is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage   | tea     | cola    | almond-milk | coffee    |
| Hobby      | vegafina | bolivar | havana      | tiparillo |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-3::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, spy, romance, fantasy
There 4 different types of food: artichoke, avocado, mango, pumpkin
1. the person watching romance movies is somewhere to the left of the person eating mango##5
2. the person eating artichoke is somewhere to the right of the person watching romance movies##5
3. the person watching spy movies is on the left of the person watching romance movies##1
4. the person watching spy movies is on the far left##1
5. the person watching epic movies is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1
6. the person watching romance movies is on the left of the person eating artichoke##1
7. the person eating artichoke is not to the left of the person eating avocado##8
8. the person watching spy movies and the person eating avocado have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |     3     |   4   |
| Beverage   | spy    | romance   | epic    | fantasy  |
| Food       | avocado | pumpkin | artichoke | mango |

