.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-4::.
There 4 different types of food: peach, pumpkin, onion, watermelon
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: hip-hop, indie, reggae, trance
1. the fan hip-hop is the person eating pumpkin##1
2. the fan indie is on the right of the fan reggae##1
3. the fan indie is somewhere to the left of the person eating pumpkin##5
4. the fan trance is on the left or right of the person eating onion##3
5. the fan indie is on the left of the person eating peach##1
6. the person eating watermelon and the fan trance have the same parity positions##9
7. the person eating onion is on the left or right of the person eating peach##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |       2        |   3    |     4      |
| Job           | watermelon | onion | peach  | pumpkin |
| Music-Genre   | reggae             | indie          | trance | hip-hop    |

