.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-8::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, lily, zinnia, aconite
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: lacrosse, sailing, skateboarding, soccer
1. the person who growslily is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is sailing##5
2. the person who's sport is soccer is between the person who's sport is sailing and the person who's sport is skateboarding##2
3. the person who's sport is soccer and the person who growsaconite have different parity positions##9
4. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
5. the person who growsaconite is not to the right of the person who growszinnia##8
6. the person who growslily is somewhere to the left of the person who growszinnia##5
7. the person who growsaconite is somewhere to the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |       3       |    4     |
| Music-Genre   | balloon-flower    | lily | aconite         | zinnia     |
| Sport         | sailing | soccer  | skateboarding | lacrosse |

