.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-9::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: filmmaking, gardening, singing, woodworking
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skateboarding, swimming, rowing, volleyball
1. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is somewhere between the person who's sport is skateboarding and the person who's sport is swimming##7
2. the person who's sport is swimming is not to the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##8
3. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the person who's sport is rowing##1
4. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
5. the person who's hobby is gardening is not the person who's sport is skateboarding##6
6. the person who's hobby is singing is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##5
7. the person who's hobby is woodworking and the person who's sport is volleyball have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby   | woodworking | gardening | filmmaking | singing |
| Pet     | swimming     | rowing     | volleyball     | skateboarding    |

