3. the person who's hobby is skydiving is the person playing canasta##1
4. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks and the person playing chess have different parity positions##9
5. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2     |      3       |     4     |
