4. the person who likes lavender and the person who's hobby is skydiving have the same parity positions##9
5. the person who likes light-blue is on the right of the person who likes lavender##1
6. the person who's hobby is puzzles is the person who likes ivory##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |      2      |       3       |    4     |
